**Microsoft Learn** (Boost Your Tech Skills)

Microsoft Learn offers free, self-paced courses, tutorials, and learning paths for developers, IT professionals, and data engineers. You can explore cloud solutions, AI, DevOps, and more, with interactive exercises and real-world projects. Complete courses and earn certifications to validate your skills.

Link: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/

