**Monster**
Monster.com is a global job search website connecting candidates with employers across industries.
It offers job listings, resume building, salary tools, and career advice to help users find the right role.
Best for broad job searches and beginner-friendly tools, though it’s more general compared to niche tech platforms.

Link: https://www.monster.com/



